### еҫҢз«Ҝиҷ•зҗҶеҮҪж•ё
```php
// WebSocketж¶ҲжҒҜиҷ•зҗҶеҷЁжҳ е°„
class MessageHandler {
    private $handlers = [
        'join_room' => 'handleJoinRoom',
        'leave_room' => 'handleLeaveRoom',
        'code_change' => 'handleCodeChange',
        'cursor_position' => 'handleCursorPosition',
        'conflict_resolution' => 'handleConflictResolution',
        'chat_message' => 'handleChatMessage'
    ];
    
    public function handleMessage($connection, $message) {
        $data = json_decode($message, true);
        $type = $data['type'] ?? null;
        
        if (isset($this->handlers[$type])) {
            $handler = $this->handlers[$type];
            $this->$handler($connection, $data);
        }
    }
}
```

## еҮҪж•ёиӘҝз”ЁиҰҸзҜ„

### еүҚз«ҜAPIиӘҝз”ЁжЁЎжқҝ
```javascript
class APIClient {
    constructor(baseUrl) {
        this.baseUrl = baseUrl;
    }
    
    async request(endpoint, method = 'GET', data = null) {
        const config = {
            method: method,
            headers: {
                'Content-Type': 'application/json',
                'X-Requested-With': 'XMLHttpRequest'
            }
        };
        
        if (data && method !== 'GET') {
            config.body = JSON.stringify(data);
        }
        
        try {
            const response = await fetch(`${this.baseUrl}${endpoint}`, config);
            const result = await response.json();
            
            if (!result.success) {
                throw new Error(result.message || 'и«ӢжұӮеӨұж•—');
            }
            
            return result.data;
        } catch (error) {
            console.error('APIи«ӢжұӮйҢҜиӘӨ:', error);
            throw error;
        }
    }
    
    // з”ЁжҲ¶иӘҚиӯү
    async login(username, userType) {
        return this.request('/api/auth.php', 'POST', {
            action: 'login',
            username: username,
            user_type: userType
        });
    }
    
    // жҲҝй–“з®ЎзҗҶ
    async createRoom(roomName, password = null) {
        return this.request('/api/room.php', 'POST', {
            action: 'create',
            room_name: roomName,
            password: password
        });
    }
    
    // д»Јзўјж“ҚдҪң
    async saveCode(roomId, code) {
        return this.request('/api/code.php', 'POST', {
            action: 'save',
            room_id: roomId,
            code: code
        });
    }
    
    // AIеҠ©ж•ҷ
    async explainCode(code) {
        return this.request('/api/ai.php', 'POST', {
            action: 'explain',
            code: code
        });
    }
}
```

### еҫҢз«ҜAPIйҹҝжҮүжЁЎжқҝ
```php
class APIController {
    protected function success($data = null, $message = 'ж“ҚдҪңжҲҗеҠҹ') {
        return json_encode([
            'success' => true,
            'message' => $message,
            'data' => $data,
            'timestamp' => date('c')
        ]);
    }
    
    protected function error($message, $errorCode = null) {
        return json_encode([
            'success' => false,
            'message' => $message,
            'error_code' => $errorCode,
            'timestamp' => date('c')
        ]);
    }
    
    protected function validateParams($params, $required) {
        foreach ($required as $param) {
            if (!isset($params[$param])) {
                throw new InvalidArgumentException("зјәе°‘еҸғж•ё: $param");
            }
        }
    }
}
```

## йҢҜиӘӨиҷ•зҗҶжҳ е°„

### еүҚз«ҜйҢҜиӘӨиҷ•зҗҶ
```javascript
class ErrorHandler {
    static handleAPIError(error, context = '') {
        console.error(`APIйҢҜиӘӨ [${context}]:`, error);
        
        const errorMessages = {
            'E001': 'и«ӢжұӮеҸғж•ёйҢҜиӘӨ',
            'E002': 'жҲҝй–“дёҚеӯҳеңЁ',
            'E003': 'з”ЁжҲ¶дёҚеӯҳеңЁ',
            'E004': 'ж¬ҠйҷҗдёҚи¶і',
            'E005': 'ж•ёж“ҡеә«йҢҜиӘӨ',
            'E006': 'AIжңҚеӢҷйҢҜиӘӨ',
            'E007': 'WebSocketйҖЈжҺҘйҢҜиӘӨ',
            'E008': 'ж–Үд»¶дёҠеӮійҢҜиӘӨ',
            'E009': 'и«ӢжұӮйҒҺж–јй »з№Ғ',
            'E010': 'зі»зөұйҢҜиӘӨ'
        };
        
        const message = errorMessages[error.code] || error.message || 'жңӘзҹҘйҢҜиӘӨ';
        this.showErrorMessage(message);
    }
    
    static showErrorMessage(message) {
        // йЎҜзӨәйҢҜиӘӨиЁҠжҒҜзөҰз”ЁжҲ¶
        const errorDiv = document.createElement('div');
        errorDiv.className = 'error-message';
        errorDiv.textContent = message;
        document.body.appendChild(errorDiv);
        
        setTimeout(() => {
            document.body.removeChild(errorDiv);
        }, 5000);
    }
}
```

### еҫҢз«ҜйҢҜиӘӨжҳ е°„
```php
class ErrorMapper {
    private static $errorCodes = [
        'InvalidArgumentException' => 'E001',
        'RoomNotFoundException' => 'E002',
        'UserNotFoundException' => 'E003',
        'PermissionDeniedException' => 'E004',
        'DatabaseException' => 'E005',
        'AIServiceException' => 'E006',
        'WebSocketException' => 'E007',
        'FileUploadException' => 'E008',
        'RateLimitException' => 'E009'
    ];
    
    public static function mapException($exception) {
        $className = get_class($exception);
        $errorCode = self::$errorCodes[$className] ?? 'E010';
        
        return [
            'code' => $errorCode,
            'message' => $exception->getMessage(),
            'file' => $exception->getFile(),
            'line' => $exception->getLine()
        ];
    }
}
```

